$ON_LVEENHANCE
Onevent CONTROL Call C_LVEENHANCE(zc) From W1HRTIM0
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_LVEENHANCE(zc) From W1HRTIM0
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_LVEENHANCE(zc) From W1HRTIM0
